parcel.description:
Web3 Music Venue for Adults & Future home to the MetaGlades comic book trilogy 

Do you want to host an event? (Music Artists, Fashion Designers, Educational Workshops, Art Auctions) please reach out to both @lowsleazy and @mindfullmania on twitter. 

Enjoy the infinity pool, browse the car selection, visit RadArt gallery and the Sleazy Section next door, but also Metaglades island art walk and the incredible underwater submarine gallery over the water.
